MembershipPasswordCompatibilityMode Enum

Definition

Enumerates the password-compatibility modes for ASP.NET membership.

In this Article

public enum MembershipPasswordCompatibilityMode
Inheritance
Object
ValueType
System.Enum
MembershipPasswordCompatibilityMode

Remarks

This enumeration provides backward compatibility for password formats.

Fields

Framework20

Passwords are in ASP.NET 2.0 mode.
Framework40

Passwords are in ASP.NET 4 mode.
